(11, 1, 'Villa Maharaj', 'villa-maharaj', 1, 0, '<p>The spacious Villa Maharaj is located in sophisticated area Oberoi. This luxury villa is just minutes away from the famous restaurant La Lucciola, The Living Room and Ku De Ta. The gorgeous Oberoi Beach can be reached by foot makes you are able to enjoy its sunset view or walk on the sand. Wonderful could be your first impression when you step in Villa Maharaj. The background is just beautiful, covered by the greens and high walls while the color of blue sky creates heavenly atmosphere. To meet criteria of appropriate Bali accommodation, Villa Maharaj was designed with taste and sense of art; it can be seen in each corner of the villa that is dominated in white color.</p>', '<div class="intro"><p>At Villa Maharaj – it’s all about the location. Nestled off a peaceful cul-de-sac in chic Petitenget, this gorgeous four-bedroom villa offers an oasis to escape and rejuvenate while being ideally situated in trendy Seminyak.</p><p>Perfect for family living, guests will feel immediately welcomed at Villa Maharaj where informality is embraced by a team of caring and attentive staff. This five-star service combines with a&nbsp; luxurious and comfortable hideaway surrounded by tropical gardens, an inviting 12m pool, sun-drenched rooms and tranquil sitting areas. Villa Maharaj is understated and compact, but this bijou family holiday villa is the perfect base from which to explore all beautiful Bali has to offer, or simply switch off and enjoy the serenity of your private oasis.</p><p>The villa owners and staff have created a peaceful hideaway, ideal for families, where guests feel relaxed enough to pop in and out of the kitchen at mealtimes, or discuss local customs and popular dining spots with the amiable and consummate villa manager. Modern comforts also abound Villa Maharaj with two flat-screen TVs and DVDs, a sound system, and a shaded, free-form 12m pool. There is a refreshing lack of pretentiousness and superfluous adornments, while the design of the villa focuses on natural sunlight-drenched interiors highlighting a simple yet tasteful style throughout. In true Balinese tradition, calming spiritual elements are integrated across the villa, from garlanded Hindu stone deities to a secret inner garden courtyard and the exquisite and omnipresent fragrance of jasmine.</p><p>For guests wanting the best of both worlds in Bali, Villa Maharaj is a short stroll away from Seminyak. This jetsetter’s paradise is crammed with world-class gourmet restaurants, designer spas, boutiques and hip nightspots, while beautiful Petitenget beach, with its renowned beach clubs, Indian Ocean surf and fabulous sunsets, is also on your doorstep at Villa Maharaj.</p></div>', '<div class="faclitiesheading"><p><strong>Services:</strong></p><ul>	<li>Wifi internet connection</li>	<li>Welcome drink and fresh fruit basket upon arrival</li>	<li>Turn down setup service</li>	<li>Personal service by the villa staff including full time manager, housekeeper, chef, security</li>	<li>Exclusive use of the whole villa and listed facilities</li>	<li>Return airport transfer (1x in 1x out)</li></ul></div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div>', '<div class="facdesc"><p><strong>Facilities:</strong></p><div class="faclitiesheading">Capacity</div><div class="facdesc">8 guests (4 ensuite bedrooms with 2 king and 2 queen-size beds); plus 1 nanny (or kid’s) room with single bed and baby cot.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Living Areas</div><div class="facdesc">Living-dining and courtyard area; TV room; kitchen; first-floor terrace; cottage annex terrace; garden <span style="font-style: italic;">balé</span> (traditional Balinese gazebo).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Pool</div><div class="facdesc">Free-form 12 x 4m, with shallow kid’s section.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Dining</div><div class="facdesc">Full-time chef providing a wide range of western and Indonesian dishes. Special requests, kid’s menus and other dietary requirements are also accommodated.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Communication</div><div class="facdesc">Telephone in bedrooms and dining area (local and international calls); complimentary WiFi internet access.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Entertainment</div><div class="facdesc">2 satellite TVs; 2 DVD players; stereo CD sound system with iPod dock; DVD and book library; hammock; 2 massage beds and spa menu for outsourced spa services.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">For families</div><div class="facdesc">Pool toys; baby cot; high chair; board games; kid’s menu; DVDs and pool section; babysitters arranged on request.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Additional facilities</div><div class="facdesc">Parking space for one car; laundry (extra cost); mini-safety boxes; hairdryer and full bathroom amenities; barbecue; back-up power generator.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Property Area</div><div class="facdesc">1,100sqm (total land area); 310sqm (villa).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div></div><div class="tab" id="tab1" style="display: block;"><div class="text-holder"><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Bedroom 1</strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;">Quenn-size bed, en suite bathroom, air conditioning, safe</p><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Bedroom 2</strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;">Quenn-size bed, en suite bathroom, air conditioning, safe</p><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Bedroom 3</strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;">King-size bed, en suite bathroom, air conditioning, safe</p><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Bedroom 4</strong></p><p style="text-align: justify;">King-size bed, en suite bathroom, air conditioning, safe</p><p style="text-a