(26, 1, 'Villa Jajaliluna', 'villa-jajaliluna', 1, 0, '<p>Perfectly positioned in the center of entertainment Oberoi area, Villa Jajaliluna offers more than luxury accommodation but also satisfaction for your Bali holiday. The location is just strategic; close to many fine dining restaurants such as Ku De Ta, Living Room and La Lucciola, stylish boutiques, trendy shops and many tourist attractions. The nightlife is minutes away; allows you to take pleasure in the excitement. The famous Seminyak Beach is only 100 meters from the villa that makes you enjoy its gorgeous sunset and surf with ease. With all those conveniences, staying at Villa Jajaliluna is worthy for all travelers.</p><p>First the guest enter the villa, the beauty of Bali attracts their eyes through its magnificent backdrop. The architecture combined modern Balinese elements with the best amenities and selected furniture. The villa is divided into three pavilions that set around dazzling swimming pool and next to simply beautiful garden. The main pavilion has 2 storey included 4 bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms. All bedrooms are air-conditioned and come with comfort to soothe every guest. Lounge pavilion situated in the single storey building and equipped with satellite TV and CD/DVD player and books collection that is perfect spot to get spoiled together with the family. The dining pavilion is just alike the living pavilion in shape and size. It has Bengkirai wood floor and glass door for breeze flow. The dining room accommodates for 8 people and elegantly designed for guests’delight. The kitchen is fully equipped and located in the service area with the view of garden and pool.</p><p>The services are given with smile and kindness to make you feel like home. Included laundry and dry cleaning service, 24 hours security and grocery shopping at costs. Also available in Villa Jajaliluna in-villa spa treatment and tour package with driver that can be arranged on request.</p>', '<div class="intro"><p>Villa Jajaliluna is a hidden paradise in the heart of vibrant and sophisticated Seminyak on Bali’s southwest coast. Stylish, comfortable and perfect for families with children, this elegant four-bedroom villa is just a short stroll from the beach, hidden behind vine-clad walls and shaded by coconut palms, offering complete peace and privacy in a tranquil courtyard-style setting.</p><p>The crisp, white façade of the villa wraps around a dazzling T-shaped swimming pool combining modern and colonial architecture set amidst a lush tropical oasis. Villa Jajaliluna is both inspiring and practical offering three separate living areas, an open-plan kitchen and dining room, pool deck, outdoor dining terrace and four air-conditioned ensuite bedrooms. Taking inspiration from the island itself, the designers have used beautiful light and a balance of neutral tones and vibrant colours, exotic flora, vibrant culture and local artisans to create a luxurious ambience.</p><p>Villa Jajaliluna is a peaceful oasis located in Bali’s trendiest neighbourhood with funky boutiques, exquisite galleries, fine restaurants, luxurious spas and glamorous bars at your doorstep. But with your own in-house chef, private butler, swimming pool and media room, it’s also ideal for staying in and absorbing the serenity of the villa. Whether its preparing a seafood barbecue, serving cocktails by the pool, organising a private yoga class or playing games with the kids, the dedicated staff at Villa Jajaliluna treat guests to five-star service.</p><p>Guess are also offered complimentary membership at Bali’s premier private members club, The Canggu Club, which has world-class sporting facilities, fun activities for the kids, and a choice of venues for dining and relaxing.</p></div>', '<div class="faclitiesheading"><p><strong>Services:</strong></p><ul>	<li>Wifi internet connection<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Welcome drink and fresh fruit basket upon arrival<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Turn down setup service<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Personal service by the villa staff including full time manager, housekeeper, chef, security<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Exclusive use of the whole villa and listed facilities<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Return airport transfer (1x in 1x out)</li></ul></div>', '<p><strong>Facilities:</strong></p><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Neighbourhood</div><div class="facdesc">Seminyak Beach 0.5km; Canggu 6km; Kuta 8km.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Capacity</div><div class="facdesc">8 adults, 2 children (4 bedrooms: 3 with king-sized beds and 1 with twin beds which can be converted to a king plus 2 bunk beds for children).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Living Areas</div><div class="facdesc">Open living/dining pavilion; media room; living room; upstairs lounge.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Pool</div><div class="facdesc">91sqm.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Dining</div><div class="facdesc">Western, Asian, vegetarian and children’s menu. Requests accommodated (including special diets).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Communication</div><div class="facdesc">WiFi internet access; landline for local calls and IDD; mobile phone coverage.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Entertainment</div><div class="facdesc">Satellite TV and DVD players; Denon surround-sound system with CD player; iPod dock, movie hard drive; Nintendo Wii.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">For families</div><div class="facdesc">1 high chair; baby cot; baby car seat; bottle steriliser; DVDs; games.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Additional facilities</div><div class="facdesc">Safes, barbecue, backup generator, Complimentary Canggu Club access (up to 4 guests).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Property Area</div><div class="facdesc">670sqm.</div>', '<div class="faclitiesheading"><strong>Staff:</strong></div><div class="facdesc">Villa manager; chef; junior cook; butlers; villa attendants; pool attendant/handyman; security guards.&nbsp; Masseuse and babysitter on request.</div>', '<p><strong>Rates, Other Conditions, Checking in and out</strong></p><ul>	<li>Rates include airport transfer roundtrip, other complimenteries and using villa facilities.</li>	<li>The above rates are subject to a 10% VAT and 5.5% service charge</li>	<li>Groceries and beverages are charged at cost price plus a 20% handling fee which is subject to service charge and government tax.</li>	<li>Extra trundle beds in the rooms for up to four children for a small additional cost.</li>	<li>Checkin Time : 2:00 PM</li>	<li>Checkout Time : 11:00 AM</li>	<li>Latest Check Out Time without additional charge : Until 02:00 PM and&nbsp;subject to availability.</li>	<li>Charge for late check out : Half night''s rental, Until 6.00 PM and full day rate after 6.00 PM</li>	<li>Please note that late check out is subject to availability</li></ul><p><strong>Payment</strong></p><p>When the Guest makes a booking request, the Guest must make the appropriate deposit payment to Management within 5 working days of availability confirmation. The following deposit payment must be received by Management:</p><ul>	<li>For rentals beginning more than 60 days after the date of the booking request – a deposit of 50% of the total rental amount is payable</li>	<li>For rentals beginning 60 days or less after the date of the booking request – the total rental amount is payable as a deposit</li></ul><p>If the required deposit payment is not received within the 5 working day period, Management&nbsp;reserves the right to void the Guest’s booking request.</p><p>Where a 50% deposit applies to the booking, the Guest must pay the remaining 50% balance not less than 60 days before the scheduled arrival date.</p><p>All payments must be made in US Dollars, unless otherwise agreed with Management, and must be made in accordance with management’s payment instructions as set out in the Guest’s booking confirmation.</p><p>If payments are not made on or before the due dates as required herein, the Owner or the Owner’s Representative may cancel the booking, in which case this Rental Contract will be thereby terminated without any further notice required. Cancellation charges may apply as detailed below.</p><h4><strong>Additional costs</strong></h4><p>The cost of electricity, mains water, cleaning and garden supplies, and local taxes are included in rental rates. There are generally no additional costs, surcharges, taxes, staff salaries, or management fees above the price quoted unless otherwise stated in the property description, the Guest booking confirmation or reservation voucher. If the information in any of these is inconsistent, the most recently issued terms will prevail.</p><p>Typically telephone and internet charges and provisioning costs will be the Guest’s responsibility. Gratuities for household staff are encouraged and normal, but are left entirely to the Guest’s discretion.</p><h4><strong>Reservation Voucher</strong></h4><p>Confirmation details, the Property address, contact details of the Owner or Owner’s Representative, transfer arrangements and directions to the Property will be sent to the Guest in a reservation voucher when full payment is received. This voucher, along with the Guest’s passport, need to be presented upon arrival.</p><p><strong>Security Deposit</strong></p><p>A security deposit may be payable directly to the Owner or Owner’s Representative immediately upon arrival at the Property. The standard security deposit required for each Property is stated in the Property description; however the Owner has the right to impose different requirements on a case by case basis. Access to the Property may be refused if security deposit is not paid in full. When the securi