igh season&nbsp;(Min. stay 5 nights) : June 15 - July 15; August 15 - September 15; Easter Week (29 March-5 April) ; Chinese New Year (8-15 February)</li>	<li>Peak season&nbsp;(Min. stay 7 nights) : July 15 - August 15; December 15 - January 15</li></ul>', NULL, '115.22206220', '-8.80046130', 10, 5, 1, 8, NULL, 7, '2016-09-14 20:38:25', '2016-09-23 11:24:18', NULL),
(33, 1, 'Villa Mary at Pantai Lima', 'villa-mary-at-pantai-lima', 2, 0, '<p><strong>Villa Mary</strong>&nbsp;is a luxury villa right on the beach at Pererenan, a small Balinese community about 20 minutes drive from Seminyak, the centre of Bali''s sophisticated shopping, restaurants and nightlife. The world famous Nirwana Golf Course at Tanah Lot is 3.5km to the north west. Villa Mary is one of five individually architecturally designed, 5- and 6-bedroom villas in the Pantai Lima estate. Each villa offers complete privacy and serenity, is truly spacious, and has vast tropical gardens. All of Villa Mary''s five bedrooms have ocean views.</p>', '<p>Villa Mary not only enjoys uninterrupted ocean vistas, but also charming river and rice field views. Its direct westerly aspect means that the setting sun sinks beneath the horizon directly in front of the property.</p><p>The villa has a Natural Style with modern and local twists. All five ensuite bedrooms at Villa Mary give guests sea views.</p><p>There are two spacious living areas : one has rice field views, the other is sited to enjoy stunning sunsets. A three level cinema room seats 20 guests comfortably.</p><p>There is a vast 100 sqm pool, an 11 sqm children''s pool, and a jacuzzi large enough for six people.</p><p>Villa Mary is set in more than 3,000 sqm of beatiful gardens and lawn, making it a perfect venue for weddings and other large events.</p>', '<p><strong>Services</strong></p><ul>	<li>Airport Transfers on arrival and departure.</li>	<li>Welcome drinks and refreshment towel once upon arrival.</li>	<li>Complimentary a car with&nbsp;driver for 8 continuous hours a day, exclusive of petrol.</li>	<li>Friendly and helpful staffs.</li>	<li>Butler service, who acts as major domo and concierge, also manages guests''&nbsp;household staff.</li>	<li>Highly-trained and unobtrusive security guards on duty round the clock.</li>	<li>A full laundry service is provided. Dry cleaning is available from outside sources.</li>	<li>K