l security team 24 hours.</p>', '<p><strong>Rates, other conditions, checking in and out</strong></p><ul>	<li>Rates include airport transfers, other complimentaries and using villa facilities.</li>	<li>The above rates are subject to a 10.5% VAT and 5% service charge.</li>	<li>Local or international calls are charged at cost.</li>	<li>Checkin Time : 14:00 PM</li>	<li>Checkout Time : 12:00 Noon</li>	<li>Charge for late check out : Half night''s rental, Until 6.00 PM and full day rate after 6.00 PM</li>	<li>Please note that late check out is subject to availability</li></ul><p><strong>Seasons</strong></p><ul>	<li>Low season&nbsp;(Min. stay 3 nights) : January 9 - May 31; 16 September until 19 December</li>	<li>High season&nbsp;(Min. stay 5 nights) : June 1 - Sept 15; Feb 8 - 13, March 27 - Apr 6</li>	<li>Peak season&nbsp;(Min. stay 5 nights) : December 20 - January 8</li></ul>', NULL, '115.11967530', '-8.65055500', 10, 5, 1, 12, NULL, 7, '2016-09-14 20:46:52', '2016-09-23 11:21:48', NULL),
(34, 1, 'Villa Sound of The Sea at Pantai Lima', 'villa-sound-of-the-sea-at-pantai-lima', 2, 1, '<p><strong>Villa Sound of the Sea</strong>&nbsp;is a luxury villa right on the beach at Pererenan, a small Balinese community about approx 20 minutes drive from Seminyak, the centre of Bali''s sophisticated shopping, restaurants and nightlife. The world famous Nirwana Golf Course at Tanah Lot is 3.5km to the north west. It is one of five individually architecturally designed, 5- and 6-bedroom villas in the Pantai Lima estate. Each villa offers complete privacy and serenity, is truly spacious, and has vast tropical gardens. Three of Villa Sound of the Sea''s five bedrooms have ocean views.</p>', '<p>The villa''s name says it all, for, like all&nbsp;<strong>villas at Pantai Lima</strong>, it''s situated right on the beach, so much so that the infinity pool seems to end in the ocean.</p><p>Sound of the Sea, designed and furnished in sophisticated Bali Modern style, has five double bedrooms, all air-conditioned. Three have sea views.</p><p>Like the other villas in the estate, all bedrooms at Sound of the Sea have 37 inc LCD televisions, satellite programming, DVD players and Bose sound systems. The main pool measures 20 x 5 metres with a maximum depth of 60 centimeters. The jacuzzi''s designed for the enjoyment of six adults.</p>', '<p><strong>Services</strong></p><ul>	<li>Complimentary airport transfers on arrival and departure.</li>	<li>Welcome drinks and refreshment towel once upon arrival.</li>	<li>Daily serving Breakfast.</li>	<li>Free of charge a 7-seater car with driver for use up to 10 hours a day &amp; 6 days/week (excluded petrol).</li>	<li>Free access to Canggu Club.</li>	<li>Staffs are&nbsp;highly trained, friendly and helpful.</li>	<li>Butler, who acts as major domo and concierge, also manages villa&nbsp;household staff.</li>	<li>Head chef (trained for the last 3 years by on-site French chefs)&nbsp;will design your own meals or possible to chose from villa&nbsp;