(35, 1, 'Villa Waringin at Pantai Lima', 'villa-waringin-at-pantai-lima', 2, 0, '<p>Villa Waringin rises from the renown sandy beaches of Pererenan, caressed by the ocean. An estate of exception, an oasis of serenity, a blissful luxury, enrapturing all your senses. With family or friends, immerse yourself in a rare holiday experience under the delicate care of our service staff.</p><p>Villa Waringin guarantees luxury, privacy, and serenity.</p>', '<p>Villa Waringin&nbsp;is a luxury villa right on the beach at Pererenan, a small Balinese community about 20 minutes drive from Seminyak, the centre of Bali''s sophisticated shopping, restaurants and nightlife. The world famous Nirwana Golf Course at Tanah Lot is 3.5km to the north west.</p><p>Villa Waringin is one of five individually architecturally designed, 5- and 6-bedroom villas in the Pantai Lima estate. Each villa offers complete privacy and serenity, is truly spacious, and has vast tropical gardens. Three of Villa Waringin''s six bedrooms have ocean views.</p><p>Villa Waringin has a 20 m beach frontage, which means unimpeded sea views. Simply put, you step from your garden right on to the beach.</p><p>There are six air-conditioned double bedrooms, three of which have sea views.</p><p>Furnished in Tropical Colonial style and ideal for families, the villa''s fixtures and fittings are of the highest international&nbsp;standard. There''s a spa area, complete with a professional massage table.</p><p>The focus of the vast gardens are a 100 sqm swimming pool, plus a 12 sqm children''s paddling pool, and a jacuzzi large enough for six adults.</p><p>Villa Waringin guarantees luxury, privacy, and serenity.&nbsp;And, with its spacious rooms and gardens, is an ideal venue for that special event – a wedding, an anniversary, a birthday celebration, or just a great party. There’s more than enough room to seat up to 40&nbsp;guests for a sit-down dinner.</p>', '<h3><strong>Services</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Complimentary airport transfers on arrival and departure.</li>	<li>Welcome drinks and refreshment towel once upon arrival.</li>	<li>Serving daily Breakfast.</li>	<li>Free access Canggu Club.</li>	<li>Free of charge using a 7-seater car with driver for use up to 10 hours a day and 6 days/week&nbsp;(excluded petrol).</li>	<li>Staffs highly trained, and are friendly and helpful.</li>	<li>Butler services, who acts as major domo and concierge, also manages villa&nbsp;household staff.</li>	<li>A team culinary from 3 chefs&nbsp;(trained Chefs mastering dishes from around the world) are preparing &amp; serving&nbsp;a five course dinner from&nbsp;Asian, French, Western and Fusion dishes.</li>	<li>Highly-trained and unobtrusive security guards on duty round the clock.</li>	<li>Personal Traineer,&nbsp;Yoga teacher,&nbsp;Therapist by call (surcharge), and&nbsp;Surf instructors (fee negoitable directly).</li>	<li>Arranging and serving events, party or occasions&nbsp;to seat up to 40&nbsp;guests for a sit-down dinner, and easy collaborating with host events''&nbsp;EOs.</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Facilities</strong></p><ul>	<li>Pool:&nbsp;&nbsp;an infinity 20 meter x 5 meter pool perfect for relaxing; Jacuzzi for 6 adults.</li>	<li>Living areas: a&nbsp;6 air-conditioned double bedrooms with king- , queen and prince-sized beds, incuded&nbsp;an each ensuite bathroom, with bathtub as well as shower; media/cinema room; living &amp; dining with kitchen.</li>	<li>Entertainment: Satellite&nbsp;TV LCD 37'';&nbsp;DVD &amp; Bose soundsystem; iPod docks (connected to speakers throughout the villa and the garden); substantial&nbsp;media room with a High Definition movie projection system, plus a library of the latest films on DVD.</li>	<li>Communications: an unlimited WiFi satellite broadband system; phone each bedroom; fax (at main office).</li>	<li>Sports: tennis court with night-lighting (shared);&nbsp;a gym with a variety of fitness equipment.</li>	<li>Other facilities: A generator;&nbsp;Bed linen, mosquito nets and 