(49, 1, 'Villa Lega', 'villa-lega', 7, 0, '<p>Villa Lega is perfect escape for those who are looking for exclusive yet comfy accommodation in their holiday in Bali. This wonderful 5-bedroom villa is located in the most popular area in the island, Seminyak. Five-star restaurants Ku De Ta, Hu’u Bar and Sarong are short drive from the villa. Boutiques, trendy shops and spas are spreading among the street that allows you to experience those pleasures with ease. Only 15 minutes from the Canggu Club, 30 minutes’ drive to Tanah Lot Temple and 80 minutes by car to Ubud that is famous for its art, culture and beautiful rice paddies.</p>', '<div class="intro"><p>Situated right on the beachfront in Batubelig, just north of Seminyak, the five-bedroom Villa LeGa is a masterpiece of contemporary design, offering its guests not only a superb location, but also lavish comfort, great facilities and a full team of staff including a manager, butlers, housekeeping, private chef and 24-hour security.</p><p>LeGa’s large air-conditioned living room opens onto the pool deck and incorporates a dining area furnished with a handsome solid-wood table for 12 and a fully fitted kitchen. More comfortable lounging space can be found upstairs in the TV lounge, outside on the furnished terrace, and on the intimate rooftop deck above the entrance to the villa, made for soaking up the sun and sea breezes. Each elegant, spacious bedroom is furnished with a king-size bed and fitted with a dressing area and semi-open-air ensuite bathroom. Upstairs, two master bedrooms enjoy ocean and sunset views while ground floor guest rooms face onto the pool. In the immaculate private walled garden a 12-metre swimming pool is surrounded by a hardwood sun deck furnished with plenty of loungers shaded by fragrant frangipani trees.</p><p>Dining at LeGa is a treat. The villa’s talented chef prepares tempting dishes from a suggestion menu and can also accommodate special dietary requests or arrange a sensational seafood barbecue. Less than ten minutes by taxi to the great restaurants and nightlife venues of Seminyak, Villa LeGa is also within easy walking beach-distance of Bali’s most fashionable beach venues, including Mosaic Beach Club and the trendy W Retreat &amp; Spa.</p><p>Villa LeGa is one of very few private villas in Seminyak that can boast a true beachfront location. This, plus its excellent facilities, dedicated staff, and easy access to a wealth of shopping and dining delights, make Villa LeGa a great choice for families or large groups looking for Bali luxury by the beach.</p></div>', '<p><strong>Services:</strong></p><ul>	<li>Wifi internet connection<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Welcome drink and fresh fruit basket upon arrival<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Turn down setup service<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Personal service by the villa staff including full time manager, housekeeper, chef, security<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Exclusive use of the whole villa and listed facilities<o:p></o:p></li>	<li>Return airport transfer (1x in 1x out)<o:p></o:p></li></ul>', '<div style="clear:both; display:block;"><div class="facilities" style="top:0; position:relative; float:left; width:95%; margin-left:40px; line-height:20px"><strong>Facilities:</strong><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Capacity</div><div class="facdesc">10 people (5 ensuite bedrooms with king-size beds).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Living areas</div><div class="facdesc">Open-plan living, dining, kitchen area with 12-seater dining table; furnished rooftop sun terrace.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Pool</div><div class="facdesc">12 x 4 metres.</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Dining</div><div class="facdesc">A suggestion menu of Western, Asian, vegetarian and children’s dishes. Requests accommodated (including special diets).</div><div class="facdesc">&nbsp;</div><div class="faclitiesheading">Communication</d