(64, 1, 'Villa Theo', 'villa-theo', 2, 0, '<p>Villa Theo Bali is a beautiful, exclusively decorated five-bedroom holiday home with a vast garden and a beautiful 20 meter swimming pool as its centrepiece.&nbsp;Bordering a river, in a very calm and genuine area next to the village of Umalas, in south-west Bali.</p><p>Villa Theo Bali is composed of two authentic Joglos as living area and the five air-conditioned en suite bedrooms of modern construction. Great for families, holidays with friends and even better for celebrations such as weddings, it comes fully staffed and situated only 5 minutes from the beach and 10 minutes from Seminyak’s restaurants and nightlife.</p>', '<p>Located in Umalas, this villa is 1.8 km from Berawa Beach. Guests benefit from terrace. Free private parking is available on site.</p><p>There is a seating area and a kitchen complete with an oven, a microwave and a toaster. Towels and bed linen are featured in this villa. Other facilities at Villa Theo Bali include an outdoor pool.</p><p>Batu Bolong Beach is 2.7 km from Villa Theo Bali, while Echo Beach is 3.2 km from the property. Ngurah Rai International Airport is 9 km away.&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Services&nbsp;</strong></p><ul>	<li>Complimentary airport transfers on arrival and departure.</li>	<li>Welcome drinks and towel refreshment&nbsp;</li>	<li>Fresh flowers and fruit basket upon arrival</li>	<li>Daily serving Breakfast&nbsp;in-house (choice continental or&nbsp;American or Indonesian)</li>	<li>Housekeeping service (morning and evening)</li>	<li>Night Security from 4 PM - 7 AM</li>	<li>Chef villa Theo Bali can prepare and serve dinners in your villa (24&nbsp;hours advance notice – cost of shopping will be charged extra to guest)</li>	<li>Free mineral drinking water and ice cubes for the duration of stay.</li>	<li>Available upon request with additional charge: extra car/motorcycle rental, tours/outdoor activities, babysitting, spa therapist in-house, and laundry service.</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Facilities</strong>&nbsp;</p><ul>	<li>Pool: Outdoor infinity pool.</li>	<li>Living areas: a 5 Air-conditioned bedroom (king size first quality bed) with inside and outside shower, as well as buthtub; dressing;&nbsp;Outside terrace with armchairs;</li>	<li>Entertainment: Flat-screen TV and&nbsp;Cable TV.</li>	<li>Communications: Free Wi-fi access in the whole house.</li>	<li>Other facilities: Safety box.</li>	<li>Carparks.</li>	<li>Villa Theo Spa.</li></ul>', '<p>On site villa manager&nbsp;– Oversees and coordinates the staff and property and is available to assist guests during their stay.</p><p>One full-time cook&nbsp;– Preparation of both local and international cuisine. A menu is provided, and the cook will do all the market shopping at your charge.</p><p>Three maids&nbsp;– Responsible for housekeeping duties and providing waiter service around the grounds and buildings of the property.</p><p>Three security guards&nbsp;– Their duties are to patrol the grounds and guard the entrance of the villa from dusk to dawn ensuring your security.</p><p>Two gardeners and pool attendant&nbsp;– Tending to the garden and the grounds of the villa. They ensure that the facilities of the villa run smoothly during your visit.</p>', '<p><strong>Rates &amp; Check in/out</strong></p><ul>	<li>Rates include airport transfers, other complimentaries &amp; villa facilities.</li>	<li>Villa rates are quoted in US Dollar,&nbsp;and are subject to 15,5% government tax and service charge.</li>	<li>Check-in: after 2.00 PM,</li>	<li>Check-out: 12.00 noon. Late checkout is possible at extra cost, based on availability.</li>	<li>Check out by maximum at 6 pm, 50% of the net rate is applied and after 6 pm 100% of the net rate.</li></ul><p><strong>Reservation &amp; Payments</strong></p><ul>	<li>As confirmation of the booking, villa owner must receive a 50% deposit. When your deposit reaches our bank account then your reservation will be confirmed.</li>	<li>If there is no confirmation within 1 week after the booking, Villa Theo Bali will automatically release the booking.</li>	<li>Balance payment must be received 30 days prior to arrival for low season, 45 days for high season.</li>	<li>For last minute bookings (within 1 week or less prior to arrival), full payment upon arrival in cash is acceptable.</li>	<li>Minimum stay requirement: 2 nights for low season, 5 nights for high.</li></ul><p><strong>Cancellation policy</strong></p><ul>	<li>Any cancellation received after confirmation booking is subject to a cancellation fee equivalent to one (1) night charge.</li>	<li>Any cancellation received within 30 days prior to arrival is subject to a cancellation fee equivalent to 50% of the entire reservation charge.</li>	<li>Cancellation within 24 hours prior to arrival, no show and early check out are subject to 100% of the entire reservation charge.</li></ul>', NULL, '114.51105820', '-8.45569740', 10, 5, 3, 10, NULL, 7, '2016-09-20 17:18:09', '2016-09-23 14:27:01', NULL),
(65, 1, 'Villa Jewel', 'villa-jewel', 2, 0, '<p>The beautiful <strong>Villa Jewel</strong> is located in the traditional Balinese village named Cepaka overlooking the river Pennet and facing a tropical forest. The atmosphere gives you the feeling of being in Ubud, only a lot closer to the beach. This tranquil 5 bedroom villa offers complete privacy and a perfect setting for relaxation.</p>', '<p><strong>Villa Jewel </strong>is equipped with everything you can wish for your holiday, from a media room to a games room with pool table, a private spa room and sitting bales overlooking the river and forest.&nbsp;Villa Jewel is the perfect setting for retreats of any kind as well as events for weddings, birthdays or other special occasions.</p><p>The villa is designed as a traditional family compound, it is a stunning example of early Balinese style with open-sided living areas and air conditioned en-suite bedrooms.</p><p>The Yoga Bale has a beautiful river view to ensure an unforgettable practice. In the center of the garden is a 45m2 infinity pool. Another 6 m2 plunge pool leads from the master suite.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Services</strong>&nbsp;</p><ul type="square">	<li>Private airport transfer to and from the airport with English-speaking driver.</li>	<li>VIP fast service at the airport is available upon request (extra charge).</li>	<li>Welcome drinks and towel refreshment upon arrival.</li>	<li>Serving daily continental Breakfast (2 persons/bedroom).</li>	<li>Free using a&nbsp;car (Toyota Innova or similar) with driver available from 9 am to 7 pm -&nbsp;petrol excluded (car usage beyond designated hours will be charged US$ 5 per hour).</li>	<li>Daily cleaning Housekeeping staff,</li>	<li>Professional chef for in-villa lunch and dinner is available upon request.</li>	<li>Maintanance garden and pool every day.</li>	<li>Overnight security.</li>	<li>Villa manager can arrange spa treatments, from a traditional massage, stone massage to modern manicures and pedicures treatments in the comfort of the villa at very reasonable rates.</li>	<li>Assisting to arrange&nbsp;babysitters, baby cot and toddler''s high chair to villa guests at very reasonable rates.</li>	<li>Pool fence for your toddler safety can be arranged upon request.</li>	<li>Assisting to facilitate to meet&nbsp;professional EOs&nbsp;and boutiques caterer for weddings and other events celebration.</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Facilities</strong></p><ul>	<li>Pools:&nbsp;Chlorine system;&nbsp;6m2 infinity plunge pool;&nbsp;45m2 infinity swimming pool</li>	<li>Living areas: 5&nbsp;Air-conditioned and fans&nbsp;en-suite bedrooms; open sided living and dining area; equipped kitchen;&nbsp;En-suite bathroom with indoor shower and outdoor bathtub;&nbsp;Spa Room;&nbsp;Media Room;&nbsp;Games Room.</li>	<li>Communications:</li>	<li>Entertainments:&nbsp;Satelite TV (Master bedroom&nbsp;and Media Room); Bose soundsystem; Yamaha soundsystem.</li>	<li>Sport: Tennis table.</li>	<li>Other facilities: Yoga Pavillion;&nbsp;Bale; safety box; Massage tables.</li>	<li>Extra capacity: yard for wedding and other events</li></ul><p><b>Additional Information</b></p><ul type="square">	<li>Villa Jewel is located in the tropical island and having tropical garden. The presence of small lizard (cicak) and gecko (tokek) are common thing and they are not dangerous. If the guest do not feel comfortable with their presence please call the staff to take them away.</li>	<li>As the villa having tropical garden including it surrounding, fogging is done periodically to repel the mosquitoes presence.</li></ul>', '<ul>	<li>A villa manager</li>	<li>A chef</li>	<li>Housekeepers</li>	<li>A driver</li>	<li>Gardener / Pool attendant</li>	<li>Securities</li></ul>', '<p><strong>Rates and Time for Check-in/Check-out&nbsp;</strong></p><ul>	<li>Rates include airport transfers, breakfast, a&nbsp;car (Toyota Innova or similar) with driver available from 9 am to 7 pm -&nbsp;petrol excluded,&nbsp;all complimentaries services and other villa facilities.&nbsp;</li>	<li>Rates are in USD, and&nbsp;subject governments tax 10% and services charge 5.5%.</li>	<li>Meal preparations based on grocery cost + 15% handling fee.</li>	<li>Laundry, local transportation, telephone bill and other optional (guests'' account).</li>	<li>Check-in: 2 PM</li>	<li>Check-out: 12 Noon</li>	<li>Late check-out until 3:00 PM is available for free-of-charge if we do not have other guests arriving on that day.</li>	<li>Late check-out until 6:00 PM will be charged 50% of nightly rate, after 6:00 PM will be charged at full nightly rate.</li></ul><p><b>Minimum Stay Requirements:</b></p><ul type="square">	<li>Low Season: 2-NIGHTS</li>	<li>High Season: 3-NIGHTS</li>	<li>Peak Season: 5-NIGHTS</li></ul><p><b>Cancellation and Refund Policies:</b></p><ul type="square">	<li>100% deposit refund less 1 night stay rate if cancellation made 60 days before arrival.</li>	<li>50% refund if cancellation made 45 days before arrival.</li>	<li>No refund is provided if cancellation is made less than 45 days before arrival or no show.</li></ul>', NULL, '115.14986810', '-8.59299030', 10, 5, 3, 9, NULL, 7, '2016-09-20 17:35:55', '2016-09-23 14:11:33', NULL),
(66, 0, 'Villa Mary', 'villa-mary', 2, 0, '<p>Villa Mary with its five master ensuite bedrooms, spacious living areas and beautiful grounds is ideally situated on the Pererenan beach known only to a few experienced surfers and a few local Balinese. The sunsets are stunning and never to forget.</p><p>The villa offers a true bali experience, surrounded by rice fields, a temple and small local village close by. All the hot spots of Seminyak are on only a 30 minutes drive and the Greg Norman-designed Nirwana golf course is only 4 km from the Villa.</p>', '<p>Featuring a terrace, Villa Mary is a villa, situated in Canggu. The property features views of the sea and is 900 m from Echo Beach. Free WiFi is provided and free private parking is available on site.</p><p>An oven and a microwave can be found in the kitchen. A TV and DVD player are offered. Other facilities at Villa Mary include an outdoor pool.</p><p>You can play tennis at the property, and car hire is available. Batu Bolong Beach is 1.5 km from Villa Mary, while Berawa Beach is 2.5 km from the property. The nearest airport is Ngurah Rai International Airport, 12 km from the property.&nbsp;</p>', '<ul>	<li>	<p>Our team of three chefs provides an eclectic menu&nbsp;selection offering Western, authentic Indonesian&nbsp;and other Asian cuisine.</p>	</li>	<li>	<p>Languages spoken: Indonesian and English</p>	</li>	<li>	<p>Daily maid service</p>	</li>	<li>	<p>Airport shuttle (surcharge)</p>	</li>	<li>	<p>Car hire</p>	</li></ul>', '<h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">20 METRE LONG POOL</h3><p>Villa Mary comprises two pools: One adult pool,&nbsp;perfect for relaxing and fitness measuring 20 metres,&nbsp;and another 10 square metre shallow pool for&nbsp;toddlers and infants. Both pools are chlorine free&nbsp;and kid friendly. A heated Jacuzzi near the beach-front also holds up to six adults.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">PERSONAL DINING ROOM</h3><p>The 50 square metre space can be thrown open&nbsp;with French windows and plays host to the finest&nbsp;cuisines in the world, from local Balinese fare to&nbsp;French, Italian or even Japanese, prepared for you&nbsp;by your own private chef and staff in the comfort&nbsp;of your air conditioned dining room.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">MASSAGE PAVILION</h3><p>Nestled on the edge of where Villa Mary’s beautiful&nbsp;green lawn ends and the majestic beach and ocean&nbsp;begins is the lovely massage pavilion. Drift off to&nbsp;the cathartic sounds of the waves crashing against&nbsp;the shore as you enjoy any number of ?spa treatments from a massage to manicure. Just ask your&nbsp;butler to arrange for a massage or beauty therapist&nbsp;to visit.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">LIVING ROOM</h3><p>This breezy living room and lounge is open to&nbsp;the gentle sea breezes and caters to the most&nbsp;elegant of cocktail gatherings as it opens onto&nbsp;an oasis of fresh air, pool and ocean. It measures&nbsp;100 square metres. There is also a second&nbsp;unenclosed living room on an upper level that&nbsp;has exceptional rice field views measuring&nbsp;45 square metres.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">TENNIS AND GYM</h3><p>Villa Mary has a tennis court with an all weather&nbsp;surface and night lighting for all guests to enjoy.&nbsp;A selection of fitness equipment is also available&nbsp;should you want something more strenuous than&nbsp;long beachwalks to keep in shape.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">INTERNET &amp; PHONE</h3><p>The entire estate is covered by an unlimited WiFi satellite broadband system which is yours to enjoy while you are our guest. Each of the villa’s bedrooms is equipped with a telephone, capable of local and international calls.</p><h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">ENTERTAINMENT</h3><p>All bedrooms have their own 37 inch LCD television&nbsp;screen with satellite TV programming, DVD and&nbsp;Bose sound system. iPod docks throughout the villa&nbsp;are connected to speakers throughout the villa and&nbsp;the garden. You have a large 20 guests capacity&nbsp;home cinema with a High Definition movie&nbsp;projection system.</p>', '<h3 data-fontsize="28" data-lineheight="48">STAFF &amp; SECURITY</h3><p>Your Balinese staff is unobtrusive and discreet&nbsp;but ever friendly and helpful. Your butler, who acts&nbsp;as major domo and concierge, also manages&nbsp;your household staff.</p><p>The team counts in total 12 members. All at your&nbsp;service between 07.00 in the morning and 23.00&nbsp;at night. They will be involved in housekeeping,&nbsp;garden, pool and chefs. Next to this there is&nbsp;professional security team 24 hours.</p><p>If you has a pleasant stay you are allowed to tip&nbsp;the staff. The team will appreciate &amp; accept this&nbsp;as a thank you from. Best to hand this over in&nbsp;one envelope, so all staff will get an equal share.</p>', '<p><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></p><ul>	<li>Check-In: 14:00</li>	<li>Check-out:&nbsp;11:30 - 12:00 hours</li>	<li>Cancellation and prepayment policies vary according to room type</li>	<li>Children of all ages are welcome.</li>	<li>All children under 12 years stay free of charge for extra beds.&nbsp;</li>	<li>All further older children or adults stay free of charge for extra beds.&nbsp;</li>	<li>The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 2.</li>	<li>Any type of extra bed or child''s cot/crib is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.</li>	<li>Pets are not allowed.</li>	<li>This property only accepts cash payments.</li>	<li>Credit cards are only needed to guarantee your booking</li></ul><p><strong>Seasons</strong></p><p><strong>LOW SEASON</strong><br />All remaining dates (Min. stay 2 nights)</p><p><strong>HIGH SEASON</strong><br />16 Feb – 11&nbsp;Feb&nbsp;//&nbsp;25&nbsp;Mar&nbsp;– 1st Apr // 16 Jun – 31st Aug (Min. stay 3 nights)</p><p><strong>PEAK SEASON</strong><br />21 Dec – 8 Jan&nbsp;(Min. stay 5 nights)</p><table width="100%">	<thead>		<tr>			<th>Daily rates in US $</th>			<th>Low Season</th>			<th>High Season</th>			<th>Peak Season</th>		</tr>	</thead>	<tbody>		<tr>			<td>5 Bedrooms</td>			<td>1,195</td>			<td>1,495</td>			<td>1,725</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>4&nbsp;Bedrooms</td>			<td>995</td>			<td>1,495</td>			<td>1,725</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td>3 Bedrooms</td>			<td>795</td>			<td>1,495</td>			<td>1,725</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table>', NULL, '24.79097020', '59.55653480', 10, 0, 5, 12, NULL, 7, '2016-09-20 17:53:54', '2016-09-20 22:25:50', '2016-09-20 22:25:50'),
(67, 0, 'Transera Grand Kancana Resort Villas', 'transera-grand-kancana-resort-villas', 10, 0, '<p>Transera Grand Kancana Resort Villas is a stylish retreat designed to capture the restful ambience of a traditional Balinese village. A collection of 30 luxury villas are spread across a landscape of tropical greenery in a concept that harmonizes with the surrounding environment.</p><p>The property truly anticipates the travel needs of honeymooners and couples seeking private villa Seminyak Bali&nbsp;time alone.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Transera Grand Kancana Resort Villas&nbsp; is located on the artistic outskirts of the Seminyak. It is just minutes from the island’s best boutiques as well as an excellent wining and dining scene. Seminyak’s stretch of sunset beach is just a short drive away for a day of sun, sea and Bali’s famous surf culture. The property is central to everything and the airport can be reached in 20 minutes.</p><p>The sheer size of Transera Grand Kancana Resort Villas&nbsp; makes it the perfect venue for destination weddings and celebrations of the heart. There is ample space to perform a garden ceremony before a gathering of loved ones by the main pool.&nbsp;<em>Teras Bistro</em>&nbsp;restaurant can also host up to 100 guests for an elegant cocktail reception or formal dinner.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Transera Grand Kancana Resort Villas&nbsp;was inspired by the multicultural influences of modern Balinese design in a concept that emphasizes modern home comforts with its own distinct brand of solitude. All 30 villas within the property are arranged along wide pathways lined with native flora in a style reminiscent of a small community.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Each villa is cocooned within the secured confines of a garden compound complete with a swimming pool for total peace of mind. Couples and honeymooners as well as leisure tourists and families ultimately benefit from this superb collection of&nbsp;Private Villa Seminyak Bali spaces when visiting the island of Bali.</p>', '<h3><strong>Services</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Airport shuttle (surcharge)</li>	<li>Shuttle service (free)</li>	<li>24-hour front desk</li>	<li>Breakfast in the room</li>	<li>Room service</li>	<li>Daily maid service</li>	<li>Bicycle rental</li>	<li>Languages spoken: English and&nbsp;Indonesian</li></ul>', '<h3><strong>Facilities</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Private swimming pool (6m x 3m)</li>	<li>Gazebo</li>	<li>Luxurious air-conditioned bedroom with king size bed</li>	<li>Second air-conditioned with twin beds</li>	<li>Complimentary Wi-Fi internet access</li>	<li>HD LCD TV with 60 satellite channels</li>	<li>IDD telephone</li>	<li>Mini bar</li>	<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>	<li>In-villa safe deposit box</li>	<li>Hairdryer</li>	<li>Bathrobes &amp; slippers</li>	<li>Bathroom amenities</li></ul>', '', '<h3><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Check-In: 14:00</li>	<li>Check-out: Until&nbsp;12:00 hours</li>	<li>Cancellation and prepayment policies vary according to room type.</li>	<li>Children of all ages are welcome.</li>	<li>One child under 12 years stays free of charge when using existing beds.&nbsp;</li>	<li>One older child or adult is charged IDR 450000 per person per night in an extra bed.</li>	<li>One child under 2 years stays free of charge in a child''s cot/crib.&nbsp;</li>	<li>The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1.</li>	<li>The maximum number of children''s cots/cribs in a room is 1.</li>	<li>Supplements are not calculated automatically in the total costs and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.</li>	<li>Pets are not allowed.</li></ul>', NULL, '115.17027030', '-8.67680400', 30, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, 7, '2016-09-21 22:52:59', '2016-09-21 22:52:59', NULL),
(68, 0, 'Bidadari Private Pool Villa', 'bidadari-private-pool-villa', 10, 0, '<p>Located in Kerobokan, set amidst a tropical garden, a 10-minute drive from Seminyak Beach. It features 19 villas with a private pavilion and swimming pool.<br /><br />Each villa has outdoor shower, a separate living area, kitchenette and is well equipped with a flat-screen TV.<br /><br />Guests can enjoy some pampering by experiencing a traditional Balinese massage or one of The Yubi Spa divine treatments. The resort provides car rental services while travel arrangements can be made at Front Desk.<br /><br />Yubi restaurant serves a fine selection of international and local dishes. Romantic candlelight dinner in the villa is also available upon request.<br /><br />The resort is a 20-minute drive from Legian shopping area and a 35-minute drive from Ngurah Rai International Airport. Free shuttle services to Legian and Seminyak is available.</p>', '<p>Located a 10-minute drive from Ku De Ta and Seminyak square, Bidadari Private Pool Villa offers an outdoor pool. Free WiFi access is available. The 2-storey villa has a traditional Balinese Balé and sun deck next to the pool.</p><p>The villa is provided with a terrace, dining area and two living rooms. Complete with a flat-screen cable TV, the living rooms is also equipped with a DVD player and fax machine. There is a full kitchen with a dishwasher, refrigerator and a microwave. The rooms are fitted with air conditioner, seating area and mosquito nets. Featuring a shower, private bathrooms also come with a bath and a hairdryer. You can enjoy pool view and garden view.</p><p>At Bidadari Private Pool Villa you will find a garden and a terrace. The friendly staff can assist with bike hire, car rental and airport transfer at additional charges. Relaxing massage is available upon request. Other facilities like grocery deliveries, an ironing service and laundry facilities are offered. The property offers free parking.</p><p>The villa is a 10-minute drive from Canggu Club, a 12-minute drive from Petitenget Temple and a 30-minute drive from Bali Denpasar International Airport.&nbsp;</p>', '<h3><strong>Services</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Airport transfers</li>	<li>Free shuttle service to Legian - Seminyak – Kuta area</li>	<li>Car rental</li>	<li>dry cleaning service</li>	<li>Doctor on call (surcharge)</li>	<li>Tour arrangement</li>	<li>In villa dinning&nbsp;</li></ul>', '<h3><strong>Facilities</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Air conditioned bed room&nbsp;</li>	<li>Spacious bathroom and open air shower</li>	<li>Open and cozy living and dining area</li>	<li>Kitchen with kitchenette and dining area</li>	<li>Refrigerator</li>	<li>Private pool and garden</li>	<li>Private Gazebo&nbsp;</li>	<li>TV with satellite and international channel</li>	<li>DVD player and stereo system</li>	<li>In room safety deposit box</li>	<li>Currency exchange&nbsp;</li></ul>', '', '<h3><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></h3><ul>	<li>Check-in:&nbsp;14:00 - 00:00 hours</li>	<li>Check-out:&nbsp;11:30 - 12:00 hours</li>	<li>Cancellation and prepayment policies vary according to room type.</li>	<li>Children of all ages are welcome.</li>	<li>One child under 12 years stays free of charge when using existing beds.&nbsp;</li>	<li>There is no capacity for extra beds in the room.</li>	<li>There is no capacity for cots in the room.</li>	<li>Pets are allowed. No extra charges.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Rates</strong></h3><p>All rates are valid until December 31, 2015<br />→ High Season surcharge US$ 30.00 / night for July 15 - September 15<br />→ Peak season surcharge US$ 40.00 /night from Dec 20 – Jan 05&nbsp;<br />→ Above rates are subject 21% Service Charge and Government Tax&nbsp;<br />→ All rates may change without prior notice.</p>', NULL, '115.26231410', '-8.47057190', 19, 32, 2, NULL, NULL, 7, '2016-09-21 23:07:13', '2016-09-21 23:07:13', NULL);
